@startuml IntegrationOtherDataSources
title TIMELAPSE - Outros Data Sources (RF002, RF003)
participant Timelapse
participant PluginHost
participant CustomAdapter
participant ExternalAPI

Timelapse -> PluginHost: getRegisteredDataSource()
PluginHost -> CustomAdapter: getAdapter(type: ERP/Outro)
CustomAdapter -> CustomAdapter: Implementa IDataSourcePlugin

Timelapse -> CustomAdapter: pull(checkpoint)
CustomAdapter -> ExternalAPI: GET /api/endpoint (API específica)
ExternalAPI -> CustomAdapter: JSON/XML resposta
CustomAdapter -> CustomAdapter: Map ExternalFormat -> TimelapseTask
CustomAdapter -> Timelapse: tasks[], metadata[]

note over CustomAdapter
  Addons customizados para
  ERPs e outros sistemas
  Padrão de conversão interno
end note
@enduml
